Class OrderController

java.lang.Object
lt.viko.eif.m.trojanovskis.taksi.rest.taksirest.controller.OrderController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/orders") public class OrderController extends Object
Represents OrderController Object that is responsible for GET, POST, PUT, DELETE Requests This class is responsible for handling API requests and responses related to Order
